title: Beach Boys Cannabis Company – Portland
cleaned_text:
WE ARE OPEN seven days a week!

Our storefront is open to the public, and we do not do curbside pickup.

For deliveries, please make an online order through our Weedmaps pages (search Beach Boys Cannabis Portland Delivery or Kittery Delivery).

The use of masks is optional for staff & patients who are fully vaccinated.

For pick-up / delivery orders please order through our Weedmaps menu!
